DLW-SPUN · the full weave of Thomas Covenant

who   : Thomas Covenant — The Wielder & The Despiser (the bound center of all ten books).
what  : the white gold wielder. A leper exiled from his own world; the Unbeliever who will not grant the Land is real. Guilty of an unforgivable act in the first days, and driven by that guilt ever after. Wild magic — keystone of the Arch of Time — answers his ring; his refusal to surrender it is the only thing that holds. The anti-hero on whom everything turns.
where : The Wielder & The Despiser · the bound center of all ten books, within The Chronicles of Thomas Covenant.
why   : to hold the office this roll assigns: the bound center of all ten books.
when  : across the events of The Chronicles of Thomas Covenant (as the lineage records).
